description: {"blocks":[{"key":"4ip1q","text":"Phenotyping Infrastructures are the basis to enable productive data collection and management.  Here - we describe how we constructed the PhenoRig and PhenoCage, the two cost-effective systems which can be constructed with lightweight materials to realize the high-throughput image collection to phenotype plant growth in a growth chamber or a greenhouse workspace.
